author: @AmpuniYaAllah
text:
No God except Allah ☝️💎 And Prophet Muhammad is Messenger of ALLAH 🌳🌦️🏞️

‎👑🍀🌸THE GOD, the Creator of space and earth, said: "Indeed, I am ALLAH, there is no god but Me, so worship Me and perform Sholat to remember Me." (Qur'an Surah Thaha: Ayat 14) 
‎
‎🕌 Religions other than Islam are false and false religions, created by their own ancestors. they are disbelievers, what they worship are weak creatures who they themselves pretend to be God. Creatures created by Allah 'Azza wa Jalla too. The real God is the creator of us and all of them, the creator of all the dimensional worlds and everything in them, namely ALLAH, the Most Holy and Most High 🌧️🏞️🌄🌈. Allah Subhanahu wa Ta'ala has announced that whoever disbelieves (does not believe) in HIM or is a Mushrik (worships/deifies other than Allah SWT), He will torture him with painful torment and burn in Hell, Jahannam 🔥 eternally forever 🔥🔥 ⚔️⚔️🌋⚡🌪️🍂🏜️ 🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥. 
‎
‎And who believes in HIM without shirk/polytheism (without deifying other than Allah, without considering that there is more than one Allah, without believing that Allah has children or begotten) and obeys the commands of His Messenger (Prophet Muhammad shollallahu 'alaihi wa Sallam ), then Allah SWT will enter him into His Heaven 🏞️ which is full of pleasure, eternal forever 🏞️🌻🍀💖💎🕌🌳🌺✨💙🌹🏞️.
‎
‎⚠️🌧️☔ All of this, faith and disbelief, is a test from Allah SWT. He SWT himself is the one who made all this, which one chooses to believe✅🏞️🌈 & which one chooses disbelief❌🔥🌋. To test us, humans, His creatures in this mortal, rotten & mosquito-filled world.🏔️🌄 May we die as Muslims (believing in Allah SWT and His Messenger Prophet Muhammad Shollallahu 'alaihi wa Sallam) Aamiin ✨🍀🌹. 
‎
‎Washollallahu 'ala Nabiyyina Muhammad Walhamdulillaahi Rabbil 'Alamin. Wassalamu'alaikum warahmatullahi wabarokatuh 💙🏞️.
